title: Australia: Vigilantes Slash Tyres of Coronavirus 'Refugees' Pouring Into Outback from Cities
description: (AFP) -- Vigilantes in some Australian outback towns have reportedly slashed tyres of those fleeing coronavirus hotspots in the big cities, according to a government minister who urged calm on Friday.
